14 WHEREAS, a testament to his musical abilities, Lewis has performed with Robert Lee Smith
15 and The Original Tams, Liz Spraggins, R&B great Barbara Hall, Bobby Blue Bland,
16 Cannonball Adderly, Mongo Santa Maria, Shirley Diamond, bassist Robert Popwell, and
17 numerous other international and local artists; and
18 WHEREAS, this extraordinary Georgian has contributed innumerably to the culture and
19 music of the state, making it abundantly fitting and proper that he is honored.
20 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
21 the members of this body recognize and commend Lewis Grant and extend sincere best
22 wishes for his continued health, happiness, and success.
23 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
24 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Lewis
25 Grant.
